  <h4 class="f6 tracked black-50 ttu fw4">Why this challenge?</h4>
  <p>
    This exercise piqued my curiosity from the first sentence of reading it. It did so because it involved a rather controversial topic; rating people. Having little exposure to the topic I began reading about how other companies have dealt with one-sided ratings.
    </br></br>
    And how most of them failed, miserably.</br>
    By then I was already hooked on the idea of trying to make this work.
  </p>
</div>

