<div class="text-row reveal">
  <h4 class="f6 tracked black-50 ttu fw4">User interviews</h4>
  <p>
    I interviewed three people who had worked in the hospitality industry.
  </p>
  <p>
  Before deep diving into the industry questions I asked the interviewees some very basic question about their background and their current careers, goals and motivations etc</p>
  <img src="images/questions.png" alt="">
  <p>For the sake of brevity I included some quotes that were really important in forming my idea around the design solution.</p>
